    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<p>We´re pleased to share the deployment schedule for the upcoming Analytics Cloud SDK Version 1.3.0.</p>\n\n<p>This new version introduces exciting enhancements and significant performance improvements designed to help you build even more powerful and efficient applications.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"h_01K6E1C7GF9JP2QETBV4PQP1HS\">Scope of changes:</h3>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li data-list-item-id=\"e26169c390274f6b568ec9c0e41659415\"><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LPD-55939\">LPD-55939</a></li>\n\t<li data-list-item-id=\"ec6fe9133c656664464eea0c870e0cf0c\"><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LPD-10660\">LPD-10660</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"h_01K6E1EG0VJARJ4GZA9E89CKPY\">Deployment Schedule:</h3>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li data-list-item-id=\"e928480def62faa45323ac5fd7260007e\">Internal Environment Release:\n\t<ul>\n\t\t<li data-list-item-id=\"e751703cce1284d892faa64aa141d2042\">Date &amp; Time: September 30th, 5:00 PM UTC -3</li>\n\t</ul>\n\t</li>\n\t<li data-list-item-id=\"e3bdafb943c43307b9af9be87a4a3be47\">Production Enrvironment Release:\n\t<ul>\n\t\t<li data-list-item-id=\"e776990dededbcbf3e2c47b92d1235ab6\">Date &amp; Time: October 7th, 5:00 PM UTC -3</li>\n\t</ul>\n\t</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"h_01K6E1GX6P1YQAKCSS3HHXRHCY\">Important Notes:</h3>\n\n<p>There is <strong>no expected downtime</strong> during either the internal or the production release. Your existing applications and services will remain fully operational throughout the process</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"
      },
